{"tid":2176276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華大基因病毒試劑現假陽性  《環球時報》：靈敏度高  瑞典政府圖轉移視綫掩飾防疫不力","createTime":"2020-08-27T03:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T04:37:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5d75c603f541a8c10288256ae1e69ab6bc7db61e","tid":2176276,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"瑞典政府表示，一批由中國生物科技公司華大基因（BGI Genomics）生產的新冠病毒試劑出現假陽性的不準確檢測結果，引起對華大基因新冠病毒試劑安全性關注。《環球時報》英文版試圖釋除外界疑慮，引述專家質疑瑞典政府試圖轉移視綫，掩飾當地防疫不力，將責任推在中國試劑上。<br />\n<br />\n華大基因回應事件時指，事件源於各地對試劑敏感度標準不同，高敏感度試劑檢測無病徵個案會產生陽性結果，但若低敏感試劑被當成標準，則高敏感度試劑的結果變成「假陽性」。<br />\n<br />\n內地官方《環球時報》引述武漢大學醫學部病毒研究所教授楊佔秋，力陳低敏試劑不是，稱會將中招者當成未受感染者，妨礙防疫工作，強調中國人民及公司偏愛高敏感度試劑。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，楊佔秋暗示瑞典當局將責任推卸予中國的檢測工具，以轉移國內民眾對其抗疫不力的關注（&quot;passing bucket&quot; tactic to blame China's test kits, in order to divert domestic attention on its own failure in containing virus）。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》宣稱，瑞典對華大基因的指摘存有邏輯謬誤，瑞典一方面稱試劑不能分辨極低水平病毒及陰性結果，並稱出現假陽性結果的，主要是檢測時症狀輕微甚至沒有症狀的人。《環時》稱，有輕微症狀或無症狀者（silent carriers）亦應一律當成帶有新冠病毒，當成患者。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2736285</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1e38a34e2353969e1877c8c6d6b4cf99ac7954b3","tid":2176276,"uid":191926,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"用呢個邏輯<br />\n<br />\n發明100%陽性率的試劑<br />\n肯定唔會有假陰性<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0602c47569c5fb67d431287f97031527be6023","tid":2176276,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"又係人地錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b82f2b03eb07c4c85f873bb2dae2f7b9905986","tid":2176276,"uid":343643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"贏國一定唔會錯"},{"pid":"58722334e7e0549710424b5c858fe44f9a45d718","tid":2176276,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"瑞典政府行議會制<br />\n點樣轉移視綫, 最多咪唔做下一任<br />\n好似支那終身制要霸住個位呀?"},{"pid":"d225a239aa56fc04c65154bfd640689a1bff3d58","tid":2176276,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fea3dc0f8a8129f8ed016d80046b5723bb429c8a","tid":2176276,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"責任不在我方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66eac20cc66c764d932c3ad2d30c9596399f87dc","tid":2176276,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2519af3ff25296f8dd893f9400452cde43667fcd","tid":2176276,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:32:50.000Z","msg":"其實都幾厚面皮"},{"pid":"3ec23d66d442cffdf8604fd3acdc89abb99cf49c","tid":2176276,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2705c6cc1494e9f177c301bf6217213c46fd4064","tid":2176276,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"小李老共飛刀, 香港係米用呢隻測試???<br />\n<br />\n驗左話係陽性, 其實陰性,無姑姑要14日無薪假.<br />\n有薪假都仲可以.<br />\n不過D老細唔少到飛起!!"}]}